\c 21
\s VaRevhi vanopiwa maguta avo
\p
\v 1 Zvino vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba aVaRevhi vakaswedera kumupristi Eriazari, nokuna Joshua, mwanakomana waNuni, nokuvakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba amarudzi avana vaIsraeri,
\v 2 vakataura navo paShiro panyika yeKenani, vakati: Jehovha wakaraira nomuromo waMozisi, kuti tipiwe maguta matingagara, namafuro awo emombe dzedu.
\v 3 Vana vaIsraeri vakapa VaRevhi panhaka dzavo maguta awa namafuro awo, sezvavakange varairwa naJehovha.
\v 4 Mhuri dzaVaKohati dzikagoverwa nemijenya; vana vomupristi Aroni vaiva vaVaRevhi vakagoverwa nemijenya maguta ane gumi namatatu pakati porudzi rwaJudha, norwaSimioni, norwaBhenjamini.
\v 5 Asi vamwe vavana vaKohati vakagoverwa nemijenya maguta ane gumi pakati pemhuri dzorudzi rwaEfuremu, norudzi rwaDhani, nehafu yorudzi rwaManase.
\v 6 Vana vaGerishoni vakagoverwa nemijenya maguta ane gumi namatatu pamhuri dzorudzi rwaIsaskari, norudzi rwaAsheri, norudzi rwaNafutari, nehafu yorudzi rwaManase muBhashani.
\v 7 Vana vaMerari nemhuri dzavo vakapiwa maguta ane gumi namaviri pakati porudzi rwaRubheni, norudzi rwaGadhi, norudzi rwaZebhuruni.
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakapa VaRevhi maguta iwayo namafuro awo nemijenya, sezvakange zvarairwa naJehovha nomuromo waMozisi.
\p
\v 9 Vakavapa maguta iwayo, akarehwa mazita awo pano, pakati porudzi rwavana vaJudha, norudzi rwavana vaSimioni.
\v 10 Akava avana vaAroni, vemhuri dzaVaKohati, vaiva vana VaRevhi, nokuti ndivo vakatanga kugoverwa nemijenya.
\v 11 Vakavapa Kiriyati-Aribha, iye Abha wakange ari baba vaAnaki (ndiro Hebhuroni), panyika yamakomo yaJudha, namafuro aro akange akaripoteredza.
\v 12 Asi minda yeguta, nemisha yaro, vakazvipa Karebhu mwanakomana waJefune, zvive zvake.
\p
\v 13 Vakapa vana vomupristi Aroni Hebhuroni namafuro aro, rakange riri guta routiziro romuurayi, uye Ribhina namafuro aro,
\v 14 neJatiri namafuro aro, neEshitemoa namafuro aro,
\v 15 neHoroni namafuro aro, neDhebhiri namafuro aro,
\v 16 neAini namafuro aro, neJuta namafuro aro, neBheti-shemeshi namafuro aro; maguta mapfumbamwe pakati pamarudzi iwayo maviri.
\v 17 Napakati porudzi rwaBhenjamini Gibhiyoni namafuro aro, neGebha namafuro aro,
\v 18 neAnatoti namafuro aro, neArinoni namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 19 Maguta ese avana vaAroni mupristi akange ari maguta ane gumi namatanhatu namafuro awo.
\p
\v 20 Mhuri dzavana vaKohati, ivo VaRevhi vakange vasara vavana vaKohati, vakapiwa maguta avo nemijenya pakati porudzi rwaEfuremu.
\v 21 Vakavapa Shekemu namafuro aro panyika yamakomo yaEfuremu, raiva guta routiziro romuurayi, neGezeri namafuro aro,
\v 22 neKibhizaimi namafuro aro, neBheti-Horoni namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 23 Napakati porudzi rwaDhani, Eriteki namafuro aro, neGebhitoni namafuro aro,
\v 24 neAjaroni namafuro aro, neGatirimoni namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 25 Napakati pehafu yorudzi rwaManase, Taanaki namafuro aro, neGatirimoni namafuro aro; maguta maviri.
\v 26 Maguta ese emhuri dzavakange vasara vavana vaKohati aiva gumi namafuro awo.
\p
\v 27 Vana vaGerishoni, vemhuri dzaVaRevhi, vakavapa Gorani namafuro aro, raiva guta routiziro romuurayi, pakati pehafu yorudzi rwaManase, neBhesheitera namafuro aro; maguta maviri.
\v 28 Napakati porudzi rwaIsaskari, Kishioni namafuro aro, neDhabherati namafuro aro,
\v 29 neJarimuti namafuro aro, neEni-ganimi namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 30 Napakati porudzi rwaAsheri, Mishari namafuro aro, neAbhidhoni namafuro aro,
\v 31 neHerikati namafuro aro, neRehobhi namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 32 Napakati porudzi rwaNafutari, Kedheshi muGarirea namafuro aro, raiva guta routiziro romuurayi, neHamoti-dhori namafuro aro, neKaritani namafuro aro; maguta matatu.
\v 33 Maguta ese avaGerishoni, nemhuri dzavo, akange ari maguta ane gumi namatatu namafuro awo.
\p
\v 34 Mhuri dzavana vaMerari, ivo vakange vasara kuVaRevhi, vakavapa pakati porudzi rwaZebhuruni, Jokineamu namafuro aro, neKatira namafuro aro,
\v 35 neDhimuna namafuro aro, neNaharari namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 36 Napakati porudzi rwaRubheni, Bhezeri namafuro aro, neJahazi namafuro aro,
\v 37 neKedhemoti namafuro aro, neMofaati namafuro aro; maguta mana.
\v 38 Napakati porudzi rwaGadhi, Ramoti muGiriyadhi namafuro aro, raiva guta routiziro romuurayi, neMahanaimu namafuro aro,
\v 39 neHeshibhoni namafuro aro, neJazeri namafuro aro; iwo ese maguta mana.
\v 40 Maguta awa ese akange ari avana vaMerari, nemhuri dzavo, ivo vakange vasara vemhuri dzaVaRevhi; mugove wavo wakange uri maguta ane gumi namaviri.
\p
\v 41 Maguta ese aVaRevhi pakati penhaka yavana vaIsraeri aiva maguta ana makumi mana namasere namafuro awo.
\v 42 Maguta awa ese akange ana mafuro awo, guta rimwe nerimwe; ndizvo zvakange zvakaita maguta iwayo ese.
\p
\v 43 Saizvozvo Jehovha akapa VaIsraeri nyika yese yaakange apika, kuti uchaipa madzibaba avo; ikava yavo, vakagaramo.
\v 44 Jehovha akavazorodza kumativi ese, pese paakange apikira madzibaba avo; hakuna munhu kuvavengi vavo vese wakamira pamberi pavo; asi Jehovha wakaisa vavengi vavo vese pamaoko avo.
\v 45 Hakuna chinhu chimwe chezvinhu zvakanaka zvakange zvataurwa naJehovha kuimba yaIsraeri chakakona; zvese zvakaitika.